<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">Except we have no evidence of AI being able to take over AI research anymore than we have evidence so far that automation this time will significantly reduce human labor. It&#x27;s all speculation based on extrapolating what some researchers think will happen as models scale up, or what funders hope will happen as they pour more billions into the hype machine.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44370917&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44370249%2344370917" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
